Lets Start Finding Information with the help of Shodan 

So Shodan is basically a Website in which enables attackers to perform footprinting at various levels. 
It is used to detect devices and networks with vulnerabilities. A search in Shodan for VoIP and VPN footprinting can deliver various results, which will help gather VPN-and VoIP-related information 

As user will enter to the website "https://www.shodan.io/"
There are so many features in the website is available like Industrial Research, Databases, Network Infrastructure, Video Games

There is one Special Feature of Search box 
As any user will enter any IP address or any Domain name in this search box then he/she will get the information about:-
-> Origin
-> From where it is origined
-> Content type
-> Content Date
-> Is connection alive or not
